UNIT TIME/COST STUDY OF THE PROCESSING UNIT, TECHNICAL SERVICES DIVISION,
TUCSON PUBLIC LIBRARY. REVISED EDITION.

THE 1ST OF 3 REPORTS IN A SERIES TO DETERMINE UNIT TIME AND COST ESTIMATES FOR
THE MAJOR OPERATIONS OF THE TECHNICAL SERVICES DIVISION OF THE TUCSON PUBLIC
LIBRARY. MEMBERS OF THE PROCESSING UNIT RECORDED DAILY ACTIVITIES FOR A 4-WEEK
